title: Transformers RID 2015 S01E04 720p [TankEngine]
description:
Better late than never, here's Transformers RID 2015 S01E04 in English! This is the first place and only place I am uploading it. Please feel free to share it around but give credit where credit is due.

Chapter markings are included for your convenience.

Please note that because of the way this is broadcast, it has been upscaled to 720p and so is not "true" 720p.

Video: 

720p @ 50fps (upscaled from 576i @ 25fps)
Encoded w/Apple ProRes 422, H.264

Audio:

MPEG-2 Stereo @ 48kHz
Encoded w/Apple ProRes 422, AAC

Please enjoy this show and make sure to check back next weekend for episode 4 and beyond!

N.B.:

Tags on one or two of the previous uploads were not entirely correct. As far as I know, I cannot fix this myself. Apologies for this mistake. If you search for "Transformers RID" under "TV Shows - HD", you should be able to always find my uploads. 

Also, for episode one, I accidentally tagged it as "[Tank Engine]". This has since been corrected but the original torrent still has the error. If you come across the file outside of TPB with the error fixed, it is still legitimate
